(2274, 'giclesb7@gmail.com', 'en-us', 'Tips for studying', '#67f069', '#18 | Phrase hunting', 'It?s amazing to think that there was a time I didn?t know these words.', 'É espantoso pensar que havia um tempo em que eu não sabia essas palavras.', '1111-11-11 00:00:00', '1111-11-11 00:00:00'),
(2275, 'giclesb7@gmail.com', 'en-us', 'Tips for studying', '#67f069', '#18 | Phrase hunting', 'What?s the purpose of writing something down?', 'Qual é o objetivo de anotar algo?', '1111-11-11 00:00:00', '1111-11-11 00:00:00'),
(2276, 'giclesb7@gmail.com', 'en-us', 'Tips for studying', '#67f069', '#18 | Phrase hunting', 'Our notes are there so that we can go back and review them.', 'Nossas anotações estão lá para que nós possamos voltar e revisá-las.', '1111-11-11 00:00:00', '1111-11-11 00:00:00'),
(2277, 'giclesb7@gmail.com', 'en-us', 'Tips for studying', '#67f069', '#18 | Phrase hunting', 'Writing things down, in the long-term, gives us motivation.', 'Anotar as coisas, a longo prazo, nos dá motivação.', '1111-11-11 00:00:00', '1111-11-11 00:00:00'),
(2278, 'giclesb7@gmail.com', 'en-us', 'Tips for studying', '#67f069', '#18 | Phrase hunting', 'Every time she came across a new word, she wrote it down in her notebook.', 'Todas as vezes que ela se deparava com uma palavra nova, ela anotava no caderno dela.', '1111-11-11 00:00:00', '1111-11-11 00:00:00'),
(2279, 'giclesb7@gmail.com', 'en-us', 'Tips for studying', '#67f069', '#18 | Phrase hunting', 'Look how far I?ve come!', 'Veja o quão longe eu cheguei!', '1111-11-11 00:00:00', '1111-11-11 00:00:00'),
(2280, 'giclesb7@gmail.com', 'en-us', 'Tips for studying', '#67f069', '#18 | Phrase hunting', 'English is gonna become a part of you.', 'O inglês vai se tornar uma parte de você.', '1111-11-11 00:00:00', '1111-11-11 00:00:00'),
(2281, 'giclesb7@gmail.com', 'en-us', 'Tips for studying', '#67f069', '#18 | Phrase hunting', '?No one owes us anything.?', '?Ninguém nos deve nada.?', '1111-11-11 00:00:00', '1111-11-11 00:00:00'),
(2282, 'giclesb7@gmail.com', 'en-us', 'Tips for studying', '#67f069', '#18 | Phrase hunting', 'When we?re phrase-hunting, I want you to use Post-its.', 'Quando estamos buscando/caçando palavras, eu quero que você use Post-its.', '1111-11-11 00:00:00', '1111-11-11 00:00:00'),
(2283, 'giclesb7@gmail.com', 'en-us', 'Tips for studying', '#67f069', '#18 | Phrase hunting', 'Duly noted!', 'Saquei! / Entendido!', '1111-11-11 00:00:00', '1111-11-11 00:00:00'),
(2284, 'giclesb7@gmail.com', 'en-us', 'Tips for studying', '#67f069', '#18 | Phrase hunting', 'The best way to get new phrases is by speaking.', 'A melhor maneira de conseguir frases novas é conversando.', '1111-11-11 00:00:00', '1111-11-11 00:00:00'),
(2285, 'giclesb7@gmail.com', 'en-us', 'Tips for studying', '#67f069', '#18 | Phrase hunting', 'I couldn?t care less!', 'Eu estou pouco me lixando! / Eu não me importo!', '1111-11-11 00:00:00', '1111-11-11 00:00:00'),
